data.description: If you're seeking a home with potential and the opportunity to infuse it with your personal touch, this is the one! The first floor welcomes you with a spacious living area that includes a separate dining room, a sitting room that doubles as a home office, and a kitchen that seamlessly connects to the family room with gas fireplace. The highlight is the oversized sunroom at the rear of the home, providing a perfect space for relaxation. The owner's suite boasts a vaulted ceiling, a generous walk-in closet, dual vanities, a soaking tub, and separate shower. New 30 year roof in 2022. This home presents an incredible opportunity to create your dream living space in a prime location in DD2 school district! Listed below appraised value. SOLD AS-IS.
